Project Structure

project/
│
├── app.py                      # Main Flask app with routing
├── chatbot.py                  # Common chatbot logic
├── travel.py                   # Travel chatbot logic
├── templates/
│   ├── home.html               # Landing page with bot selection
│   ├── chatbot_ui.html         # Common chatbot interface
│   ├── travel_form.html        # Travel chatbot form
│   └── travel_results.html     # Travel chatbot results
└── static/
    └── style.css               # Optional styling